{"tid":584783,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基亞連尼: 錯失很多機會就是熱刺的歷史","createTime":"2018-03-08T05:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T10:52:19.000Z","uid":55981,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0b7b2ed996625fd84afdeb1a1d75d73f8dbe15","tid":584783,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180308/large/1520466359_e4a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180308%2Flarge%2F1520466359_e4a7.jpg&h=dd3d2fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯周三晚在歐聯16強次回合作客熱刺，於半場落後一球的情況下，最終反勝2:1，兩回合計贏4:3，順利晉級最後8強。祖記後衛基亞連尼賽後指，熱刺這些年來都是一支虎頭蛇尾的球隊，所以球隊一直都非常有信心。<br />\n<br />\n該名意大利後衛說：「熱刺是擁有很好的球員，也是支很好的球隊，但我們知道熱刺總是會在比賽當中錯失很多機會。這是熱刺的歷史，他們總是製造很多機會去取得入球，但到頭來他們總是欠缺了一點點，未能走到終點。我們相信歷史，昨天在巴黎聖日耳門對皇家馬德里的比賽也看到了，歷史是很重要的，經驗也相當重要，今晚我們憑技術取得了勝利。」"},{"pid":"18fee1b07af0d6a98b0300dc309a5e7443170f10","tid":584783,"uid":166434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"未來是熱剌的"},{"pid":"36537844cdf1c33a6997f478a2b7f4dba2ac0c3d","tid":584783,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"熱刺唔講歷史"},{"pid":"55fc8cd15e62b090609ffbcdb4c1ad3f3bb70e30","tid":584783,"uid":31017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36537844cdf1c33a6997f478a2b7f4dba2ac0c3d","tid":584783,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:41:11.000Z","msg":"熱刺唔講歷史"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"冇歷史點講<br />\n有未來先係熱刺"},{"pid":"97c2654fa7685f393600523e17cbb3ef2d9c6541","tid":584783,"uid":58022,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T06:34:05.000Z","msg":"維園阿伯贏完波仲要把口屌打後生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6848dbc8b5f0bd3040c391b68faab22d4adc0b9","tid":584783,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"鞭到啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807479252deb0ea9ca8a3c23be24c968895b995d","tid":584783,"uid":3611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eec877892f3a966b3b5a7c7d0a46a5cf0422e0cf","tid":584783,"uid":7350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"收啦老屎忽<br />\n熱已經係未來既平行時空炒9你十萬八千球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}